text:
(There she is, with Mamimi...
What are they doing...?)

Heheh...
You left yourself wide open.

Ma-Mamimi-san...?
Uhm, what is it all the sudden...?

Because Hiori seemed to be overheating,
I thought it'd be good to cool her down a bit.

Heating up...?
...I see, maybe she needs to calm down a bit...

No, that was just a joke.
It's just that Hiori seemed vulnerable, so...

Hey, more ice...!
How many do you have...!?

(Seems like,
I didn't need to do anything after all.)
